Robert Keith (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Keith_(actor) 0 Robert Keith (born Rolland Keith Richey, February 10, 1898 – December 22, 1966) was an American stage and film actor who appeared in several dozen films, mostly in the 1950s as a character actor.
